            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              For year long, you want to avoid Plastic, from my understanding. It's ever so slightly permeable to oxygen, which is enemy of flavor. A 5 gallon glass carboy is ideal for bulk aging mead.

              

              
              
            </div>
